    <summary>Simple SQLite ORM with data encryption</summary>
    <description>
Simple ORM for SQLite with data encryption.
Supported Xamarin platforms:
- Android
- iOS
- Windows Phone 8.1
Just add [CryptoTable("TableName")] attribute to your class definition (Table) and [Encrypted] attribute to a properties in your class that you want to be stored in database file in encrypted view.
CryptoSQLite will encrypt all [Encrypted] properties automatically when you adding elements in your Table and decrypt all encrypted properties when you getting elements from the Table in database file.
PCL provides CRUD (Create, Read, Update, Delete) functions and Find functions.
    </description>
